Canonical website:
  https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/archive/refs/tags/v23.0.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack bitcoin-23.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./bitcoin-23.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/bitcoin-23.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/bitcoin-23.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libbitcoinconsensus0-23.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libbitcoinconsensus-devel-23.0-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(bitcoin)
  /usr/bin/bench_bitcoin.exe
  /usr/bin/bitcoin-cli.exe
  /usr/bin/bitcoin-tx.exe
  /usr/bin/bitcoin-util.exe
  /usr/bin/bitcoind.exe
  /usr/bin/test_bitcoin.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/bitcoin.README
  /usr/share/doc/bitcoin/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/bitcoin/README.md
  /usr/share/man/man1/bitcoin-cli.1.gz
  /usr/share/man/man1/bitcoin-tx.1.gz
  /usr/share/man/man1/bitcoin-util.1.gz
  /usr/share/man/man1/bitcoind.1.gz

(libbitcoinconsensus0)
  /usr/bin/cygbitcoinconsensus-0.dll

(libbitcoinconsensus-devel)
  /usr/include/bitcoinconsensus.h
  /usr/lib/libbitcoinconsensus.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/libbitcoinconsensus.pc

